5:
I thought I'd finally work toward a
dream of mine, you see.
12:
When you first reached out to
Ayumu and he began to smile
again, the only thing I felt was guilt.
15:
Awful, isn't it? Instead of helping, I
learned to give excuses for my
behavior and pretended to be
worried.
18:
But at heart, I wished I could be a
teacher worthy of his students.
35:
Sometimes, you don't phrase your
opinions well.
37:
You're still a child who doesn't yet
know how to deal with
disappointment.
40:
But you have always been kind. You
were never one to ignore a lonely
soul crying out for help.
41:
You reached out a hand, even if
your choice of words was clumsy.
45: Nah... You've got me all wrong...
48:
I just... thought he'd be the easiest to
get along with. That's all.
51:
Perhaps. But I can see there's a side
to you that you may not even know.
56:
It seems that this is my power. Was
that enough?
64:
I must admit, I wanted to be a
teacher because I looked up to the
tough one in a certain manga.
67:
You're talking about the one with the
baseball club full of delinquents,
right? My dad liked that one.
71:
...All right, Mr. Takamori. I think I know
what I gotta do.
76:
Hopefully, I can keep the cool
teacher act going...
93: Why did things... turn out like this?
103:
Show me a world where my mother
can be happy.
107: A world in which I was never born!
123: You see it now, don't you? It's all over!
126:
Just promise me... Promise you'll
save Chika! My sister doesn't
deserve this!
135: As if I'd just give up on this world!
139:
Not when I've still got fight left in me!
I'm going to put a stop to this!
143: So either help or stay out of my way!
147:
What can you possibly hope to
accomplish alone?!
160: What're you spacing out for, Ayumu?
171:
Don't get the wrong idea! I'm done
pretending to be friends with you,
okay?!
179: This is just me paying you back—
188: Are you even listening to me?!
192: I know what you're trying to say!
196:
We're gonna give this thing a piece
of our mind, yeah?
204: ...Put a sock in it. You're so ANNOYING!
213: Fine! We'll show it who's boss!
258: We'll stitch this place back together...
269:
Of course it wouldn't be so easy... Alk,
Nimbus, can you take care of it?
273:
You even need to ask? You guys just
focus on what you gotta do!
278:
Did you forget about me?! I've got a
stake in this too!
283:
Nothing's over yet... Not by a long
shot.
